-- Aval’s Sarmiento Purchases 55% Stake in El Tiempo Media Group
-- B y   C h r i s t i n e   J e n k i n s
-- 2012-04-20T14:01:55Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-20/aval-s-sarmiento-purchases-55-stake-in-el-tiempo-media-group.html
Grupo Aval Acciones y Valores (AVAL)  SA
Chairman Luis Carlos Sarmiento bought a 55 percent stake in
Colombian media group Casa Editorial El Tiempo SA from Grupo
Planeta SA, according to an e-mailed statement sent late
yesterday.  Sarmiento’s Organizacion Luis Carlos Sarmiento Angulo now
owns an 88.4 percent stake in El Tiempo, the statement said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Christine Jenkins in New York at 
 cjenkins28@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
David Papadopoulos at 
 papadopoulos@bloomberg.net  